social-media-calendar/
├── app.py                   # Main Python application (Flask + Slack Bolt)
├── static/                  # Static assets
│   ├── css/
│   │   └── tailwind.css     # Tailwind CSS styles
│   └── js/
│       └── main.js          # JavaScript for web interface
├── templates/               # HTML templates for web interface
│   ├── home.html            # Landing page
│   └── calendar.html        # Calendar view
├── slack_components/        # React components for Slack interface
│   └── SlackApp.jsx         # The React component you saw in the visualization
├── slack_handlers/          # Slack event handlers
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── commands.py          # Slash command handlers
│   ├── events.py            # Event handlers
│   └── interactions.py      # Interactive component handlers
├── models/                  # Data models
│   ├── __init__.py
│   └── post.py              # Post data model
├── .env                     # Environment variables
├── requirements.txt         # Python dependencies
└── README.md                # Documentation